quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,"Vataurire maererano nemuenzaniso wenyaya yevagari vedhorobha (Antioch (Antakiya)), apo pakauya vatumwa kwavari"
  36,14,"Patakavatumira vatumwa vaviri, vakavaramba. Saka takavasimbisa newechitatu, uye vakati: “Chokwadi, tave tinotumwa kwamuri sevatumwa.”"
  36,15,"Ivo (vanhu vedhorobha) vakati: “Muri vanhu sesu, uye vane nyasha zhinji (Allah) hapana chavadzikisa. Muri kutaura manyepo.”"
  36,16,"Vatumwa vakati: “Tenzi vedu vanoziva kuti tave tinotumwa sevatumwa kwamuri.”"
  36,17,“Uye basa redu ndere kungosvitsa shoko zviri pachena.”
  36,18,"Ivo (vanhu) vakati: “Isu tiri kuona chiitiko chakaipa (munyama) kubva kwamuri. Mukasasiya, tinoku temai-temai nematombo zvechokwadi, uye marwadzo akaomarara anokuwanai kubva kwatiri.”"
  36,19,"(Ivo vatumwa) vakati: “(Munyama) Zviitiko zvenyu zvakaipa zvinemi! (Munochishevedza kuti “chiitiko chakaipa (munyama)”) nekuti murikueuchidzwa? Asi muri vanhu vanotyora mirairo yaAllah (muchiita mhando dzose dzezvitadzo zvikuru uye nekusateerera Allah).”"
  36,20,"Uye pakauya murume achimhanya kubva kunzvimbo yaiva kure yedhorobha akati: “Imi vanhu vangu! Teererai vatumwa.”"
  36,21,"“Tevedzerai avo vasingambo kubvunzai maererano nemubhadharo wavo, uye vakatungamirirwa (munzira yakatwasuka).”"
  36,22,“Uye ndingazotadza sei kunamata avo vakandisika uye kwavari muchava munodzoserwa?”
  36,23,"“Ndingatora here zvinamatwa kunze kwavo? Kana vane nyasha zhinji (Allah) vakandishuvira chakaipa, kumiririra kwazvo (zvinamatwa kunze kwaAllah) hakukwanisi kundibatsira, uye hazvikwanisi kundinunura?”"
  36,24,"“Zvirokwazvo, ndinenge ndiri mukurasika kuri pachena.”"
  36,25,"“Zvirokwazvo, ndave ndinotenda muna Tenzi venyu, naizvozvo nditeererei!”"
  36,26,"Zvakanzi (kwaari apo paakauraiwa nevasingatendi): “Pinda Paradhiso.” Akati: “Ndinoshuvira kuti dai vanhu vangu vaziva.”"
  36,27,"“Kuti Tenzi vangu (Allah) vandiregerera, uye vakandiita umwe wevakaremekedzwa!”"